Package: cellcuratoR
Type: Package
Title: Shares Interactive Single-Cell Visualizations from Seurat
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Andrew", "Voigt", email = "andrew-voigt@uiowa.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Scott", "Whitmore", role = c("aut")))
URL: www.github.com/drewvoigt10/cellcuratoR
Description: cellcuratoR is a package for sharing interactive single-cell gene expression
    visualization from Seurat. This package can be used to interact with Seuart-analyzed 
    single-cell RNA sequencing data interactively with the R Shiny framework.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
